✨ Features
Instant Palette Generation: Click the "Generate Palette" button to instantly randomize a fresh batch of 5 cohesive colors.

Dual-Copy Functionality: Click anywhere on a color block or on its specific copy icon to grab the Hex code.

User Feedback Animation: Icons dynamically switch to a green checkmark (✓) for 1.5 seconds upon a successful copy action.

